<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥnạnk yạrby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ḥnạnk yạrby ygẖzw ạlqlwb fạ̉nt ạlṣdyq wạ̉nt ạlḥbyb
 lạ̉jl ạlkẖṭạẗ bdẖlt ạlḥyạẗ sfkt dmạỷk fwq ạlṣlyb
 flys sẖbyh lḥbk hdẖạ fḥb ạlạ̹lh ʿjyb ʿjyb
 tḥb ạljmyʿ wạ̹dẖ yṭlbwn bkl ḥnạn lhm tstjyb
 wtṣgẖy ạ̹lyhm bṭwl ạ̉nạẗ fṣdrk yạrb ṣdr rḥyb
 tnạdy ạljmyʿ: tʿạlwạ ạ̹ly lkm fy fw̉ạdy ạlsẖfwq nṣyb
 tʿạlwạ ạ̹ly yạ jmyʿ ạltʿạby̱ fyfrḥ qlb ạlḥzyn ạlkỷyb
 ftḥt fw̉ạdy lkm yạ bny wqlby ynạdy fhl mn mjyb
 tʿạlwạ sryʿaⁿạ wlạ tbṭỷwạ fʿrsẖy mʿd wwqty qryb
 nʿm yạ ạ̹lhy snạ̉ty ạ̹lyk bḥb ḥrạrth kạllhyb</lyrics>
